'''''Angela''''' is the type [[genus]] of [[mantis]]es of the family [[Angelidae]]. The genus was described by the French [[entomologist]] [[Jean Guillaume Audinet-Serville]] in 1839.<ref>Serville. 1839. Hist. Ins. Orth. 171</ref>

== Taxonomic ==
; List of species<ref>http://mantodea.speciesfile.org/Common/basic/Taxa.aspx?TaxonNameID=1183535</ref>
